# Strict Security Rules

Project risk tier: **{{risk_tier}}**. Strict rules apply.

- All secrets must use a secrets manager (not env vars)
- External API calls require explicit approval
- Input validation required at every boundary
- Audit logging for all data mutations
- Security review required for dependency changes
- No `eval`, `exec`, or dynamic code execution
